the biggest student contingent we've ever had.

00:05:42.500 --> 00:05:45.040
So we're actually really excited about this.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:51.780
And the most important part is that all of this
happening at this conference, the sessions, the labs,

00:05:51.779 --> 00:05:57.029
the conversations happening in the halls, they're all
for you guys, and that's the really important part.

00:05:57.029 --> 00:06:01.149
So make sure that you know that, and make sure that
if you see people in the labs, don't be afraid.

00:06:01.149 --> 00:06:02.039
Go in there.

00:06:02.040 --> 00:06:02.850
Ask questions.

00:06:02.850 --> 00:06:07.730
