00:08:46.409 --> 00:08:49.549
It's going to be a great time, so we're
looking forward to having you there.

00:08:49.549 --> 00:08:53.870
So one of the real problems, or I guess
one of the real awesome things, actually,

00:08:53.870 --> 00:08:57.580
about WWDC is there are tons of sessions to go to.

