so I've prepared a small list here of highlights
that if there are a few sessions you go to this week,

00:09:11.909 --> 00:09:16.089
you're going to want to try to pick up, especially as students,
but really even if you're just new to the platform,

00:09:16.090 --> 00:09:20.300
or even if you've been coding for a long
time, these are really foundational sessions.

00:09:20.299 --> 00:09:24.250
So Tuesday morning we've got Coding
Smarter with Objective C2.

00:09:24.250 --> 00:09:27.629
I'm actually presenting in that,
